Name Catalogue REST API

	This web service namespace is an add-on to the already existing CDM REST API and provides information relating to 
	scientific names as well as taxa present in the underlying datasource.
	
	The services include,
		
		*** {{{./remote/name-catalogue-default.html} name search}} 		: This web service endpoint serves as a search engine for 
	scientific name-related taxonomic information.
	
		*** {{{./remote/name-catalogue-name-info.html} name information}}	: This web service endpoint provides information related a specific name uuid.
	
		*** {{{./remote/name-catalogue-taxon-info.html} taxon information}} 	: This web service endpoint provides information related a specific taxon uuid.
		
		*** {{{./remote/name-catalogue-accepted.html} accepted name search}} 	: This web service endpoint serves as a search engine for retrieving taxonomic information of the accepted name of the synonomy to which the queried scientific name belongs. 
		
		*** {{{./remote/name-catalogue-fuzzy.html} fuzzy name search}} 	: This web service endpoint serves as a fuzzy search for taxonomic names.
	
	[]
	
	These web services have been developed within the i4Life project ({{{http://www.i4life.eu}http://www.i4life.eu}}) using data imported from the 
	Catalogue of Life ({{{http://www.catalogueoflife.org}http://www.catalogueoflife.org}}).
	
